{"talk":{"id":50586,"name":"Joy Wolfram: How nanoparticles could change the way we treat cancer","description":"Ninety-nine percent of cancer drugs never make it to tumors, getting washed out of the body before they have time to do their job. How can we better deliver life-saving drugs? Cancer researcher Joy Wolfram shares cutting-edge medical research into nanoparticles -- tiny particles that could be used to deliver drugs accurately to tumors -- and explains how they could keep drugs in the body longer to attack malignant cells.","slug":"joy_wolfram_how_nanoparticles_could_change_the_way_we_treat_cancer","recorded_at":"2018-10-20 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-10-18 19:44:29","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:40:49","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":613,"name":"TEDxJacksonville"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/da79a0dbaafe8543adbe4cc8060056d681510ceb_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/da79a0dbaafe8543adbe4cc8060056d681510ceb_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/da79a0dbaafe8543adbe4cc8060056d681510ceb_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/da79a0dbaafe8543adbe4cc8060056d681510ceb_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/8448227657d842e40715890f70ef44c0bd93c422_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/JoyWolfram_2018X-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":5386433,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/JoyWolfram_2018X-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":14911489,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/JoyWolfram_2018X-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":26415366,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri":"h